BEGIN:VCALENDAR
VERSION:2.0
PRODID:-//Predictor Ingest//Pipeline Schedule//EN
CALSCALE:GREGORIAN
METHOD:PUBLISH
X-WR-CALNAME:Predictor Ingest Pipeline
X-WR-TIMEZONE:America/New_York
BEGIN:VTIMEZONE
TZID:America/New_York
BEGIN:DAYLIGHT
TZOFFSETFROM:-0500
TZOFFSETTO:-0400
TZNAME:EDT
DTSTART:19700308T020000
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY;BYMONTH=3;BYDAY=2SU
END:DAYLIGHT
BEGIN:STANDARD
TZOFFSETFROM:-0400
TZOFFSETTO:-0500
TZNAME:EST
DTSTART:19701101T020000
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY;BYMONTH=11;BYDAY=1SU
END:STANDARD
END:VTIMEZONE
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:daily-pipeline-run@predictor-ingest
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260309T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260309T133000
RRULE:FREQ=DAILY
SUMMARY:Run Daily Pipeline (AI + Biosafety)
DESCRIPTION:Run both domain pipelines:\n\n  make daily\n  make daily DOMAIN=biosafety\n\nThen review extraction logs for errors.\nCheck data/extractions/ for new output.
CATEGORIES:Pipeline
STATUS:CONFIRMED
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT10M
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Pipeline run in 10 minutes
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:weekly-quality-review@predictor-ingest
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260313T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260313T160000
RRULE:FREQ=WEEKLY;BYDAY=FR
SUMMARY:Weekly Quality Review
DESCRIPTION:Review extraction quality metrics for both domains:\n\n  python scripts/collect_metrics_gist.py\n  python scripts/collect_metrics_gist.py --domain biosafety\n\nCheck:\n- Evidence fidelity rates\n- Orphan endpoint counts\n- Entity resolution drift\n- Feed health / 404s\n- Trend scoring sanity
CATEGORIES:Quality
STATUS:CONFIRMED
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT15M
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Quality review in 15 minutes
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:sprint-7-whats-hot@predictor-ingest
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260310T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260310T110000
SUMMARY:Sprint 7 - What's Hot Feature
DESCRIPTION:Next sprint: What's Hot feature (Days 12-15)\n\n7.1 Velocity delta computation in export script\n7.2 Include velocity delta in graph JSON export\n7.3 whats-hot.js ranked list UI component\n7.4 Toolbar button + keyboard shortcut (h)\n7.5 Fly-to-neighborhood on item click\n7.6 Panel CSS for hot list drawer\n\nSee: docs/project-plan.md Sprint 7
CATEGORIES:Sprint
STATUS:TENTATIVE
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:target-completion@predictor-ingest
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260315T000000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260316T000000
SUMMARY:V1 Target Completion (mid-March)
DESCRIPTION:Revised target for completing Sprints 7-11.\n\nRemaining:\n- Sprint 7: What's Hot\n- Sprint 8: Discovery Rewards\n- Sprint 9: Guided Entry\n- Sprint 10: Medium Gap Features\n- Sprint 11: Branding & Wrap-up\n\nBackend track items (B.8-B.11) may extend beyond this date.\n\nSee: docs/project-plan.md Progress Summary
CATEGORIES:Milestone
STATUS:TENTATIVE
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR
